syntax on
set relativenumber number

""" Workman Keybinds 
    nnoremap y h|xnoremap y h|onoremap y h|
    nnoremap n j|xnoremap n j|onoremap n j|
    nnoremap e k|xnoremap e k|onoremap e k|
    nnoremap o l|xnoremap o l|onoremap o l|
    nnoremap j y|xnoremap j y|onoremap j y|
    nnoremap h e|xnoremap h e|onoremap h e|
    nnoremap H E|xnoremap H E|onoremap H E|
    nnoremap l o|xnoremap l o|onoremap l o|
    nnoremap L O|xnoremap L O|onoremap L O|
    nnoremap k n|xnoremap k n|onoremap k n|
    nnoremap K N|xnoremap K N|onoremap K N|

""" Scroll down/up and append new line in INSERT Mode
    nnoremap <C-N>  <C-E>|xnoremap <C-N>  <C-E>|onoremap <C-N>  <C-E>|
    nnoremap <C-E>  <C-Y>|xnoremap <C-E>  <C-Y>|onoremap <C-E>  <C-Y>|
    nnoremap <C-L>  <C-J>|xnoremap <C-L>  <C-J>|onoremap <C-L>  <C-J>|
